§r\n\n为使用默认迷雾颜色的末地生物群系更新迷雾颜色。","option.enderscape.ambience_update_foliage_colors":"环境：更新树叶颜色","option.enderscape.ambience_update_foliage_colors.desc":"§e仅在重启后生效！§r\n\n为使用默认树叶颜色的末地生物群系更新树叶颜色。","option.enderscape.ambience_update_grass_colors":"环境：更新草颜色","option.enderscape.ambience_update_grass_colors.desc":"§e仅在重启后生效！§r\n\n为使用默认草颜色的末地生物群系更新草颜色。","option.enderscape.ambience_update_loop_sounds":"环境：更新循环音效","option.enderscape.ambience_update_loop_sounds.desc":"§e仅在重启后生效！§r\n\n为缺乏环境循环音效或使用诡异森林循环音效的末地生物群系添加环境循环音效。","option.enderscape.ambience_update_mood_sounds":"环境：更新氛围音效","option.enderscape.ambience_update_mood_sounds.desc":"§e仅在重启后生效！§r\n\n为缺乏环境氛围音效或使用诡异森林氛围音效的末地生物群系添加环境氛围音效。","option.enderscape.ambience_update_music_pools":"环境：更新音乐库","option.enderscape.ambience_update_music_pools.desc":"§e仅在重启后生效！§r\n\n更新末地生物群系的音乐库，以加入Enderscape的音乐。","option.enderscape.ambience_update_particles":"环境：更新粒子","option.enderscape.ambience_update_particles.desc":"§e仅在重启后生效！§r\n\n为缺乏环境粒子的末地生物群系添加环境粒子。","option.enderscape.ambience_update_sky_colors":"环境：更新天空颜色","option.enderscape.ambience_update_sky_colors.desc":"§e仅在重启后生效！§r\n\n为使用默认天空颜色的末地生物群系更新天空颜色。","option.enderscape.ambience_update_water_colors":"环境：更新水颜色","option.enderscape.ambience_update_water_colors.desc":"§e仅在重启后生效！§r\n\n为使用默认水颜色的末地生物群系更新水颜色。","option.enderscape.ambience_update_water_fog_colors":"环境：更新水下迷雾颜色","option.enderscape.ambience_update_water_fog_colors.desc":"§e仅在重启后生效！§r\n\n为使用默认水下迷雾颜色的末地生物群系更新水下迷雾颜色。","option.enderscape.block_sounds_update_chorus":"方块音效：更新紫颂植株和紫颂花","option.enderscape.block_sounds_update_chorus.desc":"§e仅在重启后生效！§r\n\n更新紫颂植株和紫颂花，使其听起来像干燥、粗糙的木头。","option.enderscape.block_sounds_update_end_portal_frame":"方块音效：更新末地传送门框架","option.enderscape.block_sounds_update_end_portal_frame.desc":"§e仅在重启后生效！§r\n\n更新末地传送门框架，使其发出独特音效。","option.enderscape.block_sounds_update_end_portals":"方块音效：更新末地传送门和末地折跃门","option.enderscape.block_sounds_update_end_portals.desc":"§e仅在重启后生效！§r\n\n更新末地传送门和末地折跃门方块，使其发出独特音效。","option.enderscape.block_sounds_update_end_rods":"方块音效：更新末地烛","option.enderscape.block_sounds_update_end_rods.desc":"§e仅在重启后生效！§r\n\n更新末地烛，使其听起来像清脆、摇晃的细杆。","option.enderscape.block_sounds_update_end_stone":"方块音效：更新末地石","option.enderscape.block_sounds_update_end_stone.desc":"§e仅在重启后生效！§r\n\n更新末地石，使其听起来像致密、略具肥沃度的石头。","option.enderscape.block_sounds_update_end_stone_bricks":"方块音效：更新末地石砖","option.enderscape.block_sounds_update_end_stone_bricks.desc":"§e仅在重启后生效！§r\n\n更新末地石砖，使其听起来像致密、沉重的砖块。","option.enderscape.block_sounds_update_purpur":"方块音效：更新紫珀块","option.enderscape.block_sounds_update_purpur.desc":"§e仅在重启后生效！§r\n\n更新紫珀块，使其听起来像瓷砖。","option.enderscape.block_sounds_update_shulker_boxes":"方块音效：更新潜影盒","option.enderscape.block_sounds_update_shulker_boxes.desc":"§e仅在重启后生效！§r\n\n更新潜影盒，使其听起来更像潜影贝。","option.enderscape.category.clientside":"客户端","option.enderscape.category.serverside":"服务端","option.enderscape.chorus_flower_humming":"紫颂花：添加嗡嗡作响","option.enderscape.chorus_flower_humming.desc":"启用后，紫颂花偶尔会发出低沉的嗡鸣声。","option.enderscape.chorus_flower_pollen":"紫颂花：添加花粉","option.enderscape.chorus_flower_pollen.desc":"启用后，紫颂花会释放花粉粒子。","option.enderscape.creative_tab_enabled":"启用“Enderscape”标签页","option.enderscape.creative_tab_enabled.desc":"§e仅在重进世界后生效！§r\n\n启用后，Enderscape将拥有专属的创造模式标签页，其中包含所有来自Enderscape的物品以及相关的原版物品。","option.enderscape.debug_hud_client_info":"调试HUD：客户端信息","option.enderscape.debug_hud_client_info.desc":"","option.enderscape.debug_hud_enabled":"调试HUD：启用","option.enderscape.debug_hud_enabled.desc":"","option.enderscape.debug_hud_music_info":"调试HUD：音乐信息","option.enderscape.debug_hud_music_info.desc":"","option.enderscape.debug_hud_player_info":"调试HUD：玩家信息","option.enderscape.debug_hud_player_info.desc":"","option.enderscape.debug_magnia_sprout_hitboxes":"显示磁胞芽范围判定箱","option.enderscape.debug_magnia_sprout_hitboxes.desc":"","option.enderscape.default_data_pack_fix_levitation_advancement":"默认启用“修复飘浮进度”","option.enderscape.default_data_pack_fix_levitation_advancement.desc":"§e仅在重启后生效！","option.enderscape.default_data_pack_fix_vanilla_recipes":"默认启用“修复配方冲突”","option.enderscape.default_data_pack_fix_vanilla_recipes.desc":"§e仅在重启后生效！","option.enderscape.default_data_pack_new_end_cities":"默认启用“改进末地城”","option.enderscape.default_data_pack_new_end_cities.desc":"§e仅在重启后生效！","option.enderscape.default_data_pack_new_strongholds":"默认启用“改进要塞”","option.enderscape.default_data_pack_new_strongholds.desc":"§e仅在重启后生效！","option.enderscape.default_data_pack_new_terrain":"默认启用“改进末地地形”","option.enderscape.default_data_pack_new_terrain.desc":"§e仅在重启后生效！","option.enderscape.default_resource_pack_dark_lighting":"默认启用“午夜末地光照”","option.enderscape.default_resource_pack_dark_lighting.desc":"§e仅在重启后生效！","option.enderscape.default_resource_pack_lighting":"默认启用“改进末地光照”","option.enderscape.default_resource_pack_lighting.desc":"§e仅在重启后生效！","option.enderscape.elytra_add_fov_effects":"鞘翅：添加视场角效果","option.enderscape.elytra_add_fov_effects.desc":"启用后，使用鞘翅滑翔将影响你的视场角。","option.enderscape.elytra_add_gliding_sound":"鞘翅：添加滑翔音效","option.enderscape.elytra_add_gliding_sound.desc":"启用后，使用鞘翅滑翔时将播放新的滑翔音效。\n\n其他玩家也能从远处听见它！","option.enderscape.elytra_add_open_close_sounds":"鞘翅：添加展开和收起音效","option.enderscape.elytra_add_open_close_sounds.desc":"启用后，展开和收起你的鞘翅时将播放全新音效。","option.enderscape.elytra_fov_effect_intensity":"鞘翅：视场角效果强度","option.enderscape.elytra_fov_effect_intensity.desc":"","option.enderscape.elytra_sneak_to_stop_gliding":"鞘翅：潜行以停止滑翔","option.enderscape.elytra_sneak_to_stop_gliding.desc":"启用后，按下潜行键即可立即停止滑翔。","option.enderscape.elytra_update_equip_sound":"鞘翅：更新装备音效","option.enderscape.elytra_update_equip_sound.desc":"启用后，装备鞘翅时将拥有独特音效。","option.enderscape.end_portal_update_particles":"末地传送门：更新粒子","option.enderscape.end_portal_update_particles.desc":"启用后，末地传送门将拥有独特的粒子效果。","option.enderscape.end_portal_update_travel_sound":"末地传送门：更新传送音效","option.enderscape.end_portal_update_travel_sound.desc":"启用后，传送到末地时将伴随独特的音效。","option.enderscape.ender_pearl_add_particles":"末影珍珠：添加粒子","option.enderscape.ender_pearl_add_particles.desc":"启用后，末影珍珠在空中飞行时会生成传送门粒子。","option.enderscape.ender_pearl_break_particles":"末影珍珠：破裂粒子效果","option.enderscape.ender_pearl_break_particles.desc":"启用后，末影珍珠落地时会像鸡蛋一样产生破裂粒子。","option.enderscape.ender_pearl_update_teleport_sound":"末影珍珠：更新传送音效","option.enderscape.ender_pearl_update_teleport_sound.desc":"启用后，末影珍珠的传送音效将得到更新。","option.enderscape.ender_pearl_update_throw_sound":"末影珍珠：更新投掷音效","option.enderscape.ender_pearl_update_throw_sound.desc":"启用后，末影珍珠将拥有独特的投掷音效。","option.enderscape.enderman_static_overlay":"末影人：注视时静电干扰覆盖层","option.enderscape.enderman_static_overlay.desc":"启用后，注视末影人会使你的视觉逐渐失真。","option.enderscape.enderman_static_sound":"末影人：注视时静电干扰音效","option.enderscape.enderman_static_sound.desc":"启用后，注视末影人会使你的听觉逐渐失真。","option.enderscape.enderman_stereo_stare_sound":"末影人：立体注视音效","option.enderscape.enderman_stereo_stare_sound.desc":"启用后，末影人的注视音效将与激怒它们的玩家绑定。\n\n当末影人被击败或其愤怒平息时，音效会迅速消散。","option.enderscape.endermite_emissive_eyes":"末影螨：发光的眼睛","option.enderscape.endermite_emissive_eyes.desc":"启用后，末影螨的眼睛将具有发光效果。","option.enderscape.endermite_expand_hit_range":"末影螨：扩大命中范围","option.enderscape.endermite_expand_hit_range.desc":"启用后，末影螨将更容易被命中。","option.enderscape.endermite_natural_spawns_obey_light_level":"末影螨：仅在黑暗区域自然生成","option.enderscape.endermite_natural_spawns_obey_light_level.desc":"启用后，末影螨仅会在黑暗区域自然生成。通常情况下，它们会忽略光照等级。\n\n此变更不适用于刷怪笼和试炼刷怪笼。","option.enderscape.endermite_update_sounds":"末影螨：更新音效","option.enderscape.endermite_update_sounds.desc":"启用后，末影螨将拥有独特的音效。","option.enderscape.flash_enabled":"末地闪光：启用","option.enderscape.flash_enabled.desc":"§e启用末地闪光，新增于1.21.9版本。§r\n\n偶尔，末地的天空会闪现一道耀眼的光芒。","option.enderscape.flash_frequency":"末地闪光：频率（以分钟为单位）","option.enderscape.flash_frequency.desc":"末地闪光频率（以分钟为单位）。（0.5即30秒）","option.enderscape.flash_influences_skybox":"末地闪光：影响天空盒颜色","option.enderscape.flash_influences_skybox.desc":"§e需要启用天空盒更新！§r\n\n启用后，末地闪光将使天空变暗。","option.enderscape.flash_updated_visuals":"末地闪光：更新视觉效果","option.enderscape.flash_updated_visuals.desc":"启用后，末地闪光将拥有全新纹理和生物群系特有的色彩。","option.enderscape.include_items_in_vanilla_creative_tabs":"在原版标签页中包含Enderscape物品","option.enderscape.include_items_in_vanilla_creative_tabs.desc":"§e仅在重进世界后生效！§r\n\n启用后，Enderscape的物品将出现在原版创造模式标签页中。","option.enderscape.lighting_style":"光照风格","option.enderscape.lighting_style.desc":"选择不同的光照风格。\n\n原版：不变。\n\n改进：更暗沉、更阴郁。\n\n午夜：非常暗沉、非常阴郁。","option.enderscape.mirror_screen_effect_enabled":"魔镜：显示传送覆盖层效果","option.enderscape.mirror_screen_effect_enabled.desc":"启用后，使用魔镜传送时将显示独特的屏幕效果。","option.enderscape.mirror_screen_effect_overlay_intensity":"魔镜：传送覆盖层亮度","option.enderscape.mirror_screen_effect_overlay_intensity.desc":"","option.enderscape.mirror_screen_effect_vignette_intensity":"魔镜：传送晕影强度","option.enderscape.mirror_screen_effect_vignette_intensity.desc":"","option.enderscape.mirror_tooltip_display_coordinates":"魔镜：显示连接的坐标","option.enderscape.mirror_tooltip_display_coordinates.desc":"显示魔镜所连接的方块的坐标。","option.enderscape.mirror_tooltip_display_dimension":"魔镜：显示连接的维度","option.enderscape.mirror_tooltip_display_dimension.desc":"显示魔镜所连接的方块的维度。","option.enderscape.mirror_tooltip_display_distance":"魔镜：显示连接位置的距离","option.enderscape.mirror_tooltip_display_distance.desc":"显示与魔镜所连接的方块的大致距离。","option.enderscape.mirror_tooltip_enabled":"魔镜：在提示框中显示连接信息","option.enderscape.mirror_tooltip_enabled.desc":"显示魔镜所连接的方块的信息。","option.enderscape.mirror_tooltip_shift_to_display":"魔镜：按住SHIFT键显示提示框","option.enderscape.mirror_tooltip_shift_to_display.desc":"也许你更愿意不展示你的魔镜通向何方…\n\n启用后，按住SHIFT键即可查看魔镜所连接的方块的信息。","option.enderscape.nebulite_tool_hud_enabled":"星云宝石工具HUD：启用","option.enderscape.nebulite_tool_hud_enabled.desc":"启用后，手持星云宝石工具（例如魔镜、磁胞吸引器）时，准星上方将显示一个HUD元素，显示当前能量值及使用消耗。","option.enderscape.nebulite_tool_hud_offset":"星云宝石工具HUD：偏移量","option.enderscape.nebulite_tool_hud_offset.desc":"","option.enderscape.nebulite_tool_hud_opacity":"星云宝石工具HUD：不透明度","option.enderscape.nebulite_tool_hud_opacity.desc":"","option.enderscape.portal_particle_emissive":"发光传送门粒子","option.enderscape.portal_particle_emissive.desc":"使下界传送门、末影人、末影箱及相关粒子发光。","option.enderscape.rubblemite_expand_hit_range":"碎石螨：扩大命中范围","option.enderscape.rubblemite_expand_hit_range.desc":"启用后，碎石螨将更容易被命中。","option.enderscape.shulker_bullet_enforce_count_limit":"潜影弹：强制数量限制","option.enderscape.shulker_bullet_enforce_count_limit.desc":"潜影贝同时能拥有的潜影弹最大数量。设置为0时禁用。","option.enderscape.shulker_bullet_enforce_distance_limit":"潜影弹：强制距离限制","option.enderscape.shulker_bullet_enforce_distance_limit.desc":"潜影弹在消失前与目标之间的最大距离。设置为0时禁用。","option.enderscape.shulker_bullet_enforce_owner_limit":"潜影弹：强制主人限制","option.enderscape.shulker_bullet_enforce_owner_limit.desc":"启用后，潜影弹将在主人死亡时消失。","option.enderscape.shulker_bullet_enforce_time_limit":"潜影弹：强制时间限制","option.enderscape.shulker_bullet_enforce_time_limit.desc":"潜影弹在消失前的秒数限制。设置为0时禁用。","option.enderscape.shulker_bullet_loop_sound":"潜影弹：循环音效","option.enderscape.shulker_bullet_loop_sound.desc":"启用后，潜影弹在移动时会播放新的音效。","option.enderscape.shulker_bullet_rebalance_levitation":"潜影弹：重新平衡飘浮效果","option.enderscape.shulker_bullet_rebalance_levitation.desc":"启用后，被潜影弹击中的玩家将受到更强但持续时间更短的飘浮效果。","option.enderscape.shulker_hurt_by_piercing":"潜影贝：闭合时受穿透伤害","option.enderscape.shulker_hurt_by_piercing.desc":"启用后，即使潜影贝关闭外壳时，穿透的箭仍会对其造成伤害。","option.enderscape.silverfish_delay_before_infesting_stone":"蠹虫：出现后钻入石头的延迟期","option.enderscape.silverfish_delay_before_infesting_stone.desc":"启用后，蠹虫在出现后需要延迟一段时间才能再次钻入石头。","option.enderscape.silverfish_expand_hit_range":"蠹虫：扩大命中范围","option.enderscape.silverfish_expand_hit_range.desc":"启用后，蠹虫将更容易被命中。","option.enderscape.silverfish_natural_spawns_obey_light_level":"蠹虫：仅在黑暗区域自然生成","option.enderscape.silverfish_natural_spawns_obey_light_level.desc":"启用后，蠹虫仅会在黑暗区域自然生成。通常情况下，它们会忽略光照等级。\n\n此变更不适用于刷怪笼和试炼刷怪笼。","option.enderscape.skybox_add_dynamic_fog_density":"天空盒更新：添加动态迷雾强度","option.enderscape.skybox_add_dynamic_fog_density.desc":"根据你所在的生物群系，为末地添加动态迷雾强度。\n\n可能与其他模组冲突。","option.enderscape.skybox_brightness_scale_factor":"天空盒更新：亮度等级系数","option.enderscape.skybox_brightness_scale_factor.desc":"","option.enderscape.skybox_scales_brightness_with_gamma":"天空盒更新：随亮度变化","option.enderscape.skybox_scales_brightness_with_gamma.desc":"根据游戏亮度的百分比调整天空盒亮度。\n\n旨在缓解能见度问题。大幅更改此选项可能会导致效果不佳。","option.enderscape.skybox_update_enabled":"天空盒更新：启用","option.enderscape.skybox_update_enabled.desc":"更新了末地天空盒，使其更具趣味性和动态感。\n\n更新后的天空盒遍布着细腻的星辰与星云，同时具备在不同生物群系间切换颜色的功能。","option.enderscape.structure_music_fading_enabled":"结构音乐淡出：启用","option.enderscape.structure_music_fading_enabled.desc":"启用后，进入结构时会淡出生物群系音乐，转而播放该结构的专属音乐。离开结构时，其专属音乐也会逐渐淡出。\n\n目前支持末地城。","option.enderscape.supplement_vanilla_end_city_treasure_loot":"补充：原版末地城战利品","option.enderscape.supplement_vanilla_end_city_treasure_loot.desc":"§e仅在原版末地城中生效！§r\n\n启用后，原版末地城将出现额外物品，包含Enderscape物品，例如静止盔甲纹饰、魔镜等。","option.enderscape.supplement_vanilla_stronghold_library_loot":"补充：原版要塞图书馆战利品","option.enderscape.supplement_vanilla_stronghold_library_loot.desc":"§e仅在原版要塞中生效！§r\n\n启用后，原版要塞图书馆将偶尔包含魔镜。","option.enderscape.tridents_return_from_void":"三叉戟：从虚空返回","option.enderscape.tridents_return_from_void.desc":"启用后，附有忠诚魔咒的三叉戟在击中虚空后会返回你手中，而非永远消失。","option.enderscape.value.improved":"改进","option.enderscape.value.midnight":"午夜","option.enderscape.value.vanilla":"原版","option.enderscape.void_poof_particles_upon_death":"“Void poof” 死亡时的粒子","option.enderscape.void_poof_particles_upon_death.desc":"启用后，末影人、末影螨和碎石螨死亡时会释放黑色云状粒子。","option.group.enderscape.ambience":"环境更改","option.group.enderscape.blocks":"方块更改","option.group.enderscape.client":"客户端","option.group.enderscape.creative_mode":"创造模式","option.group.enderscape.data_packs":"数据包","option.group.enderscape.debug":"调试","option.group.enderscape.entity":"实体更改","option.group.enderscape.item":"物品更改","option.group.enderscape.loot_tables":"战利品表","option.group.enderscape.resource_packs":"资源包","pack.enderscape.dark_lighting":"午夜末地光照","pack.enderscape.dark_lighting.description":"跋涉于黑暗之中","pack.enderscape.fix_levitation_advancement":"修复飘浮进度","pack.enderscape.fix_levitation_advancement.descript